Real estate investment trust Liberty Two Degrees has appointed Jos&eacute; Snyders as the company&rsquo;s new FD, effective immediately. He succeeds John Sturgeon, who will remain on the board as a nonexecutive director. &ldquo;We are very fortunate to not only have retained John on our board as a nonexecutive director but also significantly added to the team dynamic and expertise with the appointment of Jos&eacute; as the incoming FD. I look forward to working with them both in their new roles,&rdquo; CEO Amelia Beattie said.